OL,3,COld graves could be reused to manage
OL,4,Cshortage of burial space
OL,6,FOld graves could be reused under new
OL,7,Frecommendations to manage the shortage
OL,8,Fof burial space.
OL,10,FThe proposals were put forward by the
OL,11,FLaw Commission and also included
OL,12,Fgraveyards which were declared "full"
OL,13,Fduring the Victorian era potentially
OL,14,Fbeing reopened.
OL,16,FThe commission warned that urban areas
OL,17,Facross England and Wales are fast
OL,18,Frunning out of burial space.
