OL,3,COld graves could be reused to manage
OL,4,Cshortage of burial space
OL,6,FProposed changes would allow any
OL,7,Fburial ground to reuse graves, but
OL,8,Fonly following public consultation and
OL,9,Fgovernment approval.
OL,11,FSafeguards would also be in place for
OL,12,Feach individual grave, with plots only
OL,13,Feligible for reuse when the last
OL,14,Fperson was buried at least 75 years
OL,15,Fago.
OL,17,FAnother separate public consultation
OL,18,Fis considering the timeframes around
OL,19,Fgrave reuse, and what would happen if
OL,20,Ffamily members objected.
