OL,3,COld graves could be reused to manage
OL,4,Cshortage of burial space
OL,6,FProfessor Nick Hopkins, Commissioner
OL,7,Ffor Property, Family and Trust Law
OL,8,Fsaid any change would need to be
OL,9,Ftackled in consultation with the
OL,10,Fpublic.
OL,12,F"Our proposals provide a significant
OL,13,Fopportunity to reform burial and
OL,14,Fcremation law and secure burial space
OL,15,Ffor future generations," he said.
OL,17,F"This must be done sensitively and
OL,18,Fwith wider public support."
