OL,3,COld graves could be reused to manage
OL,4,Cshortage of burial space
OL,6,FAlex Davies-Jones, Parliamentary Under-
OL,7,FSecretary of State at the Ministry of
OL,8,FJustice, said the government was
OL,9,Fsupportive of the Law Commission's
OL,10,Fwork.
OL,12,F"We await with interest the Law
OL,13,FCommission's recommendations, in due
OL,14,Fcourse, on the most appropriate
OL,15,Fframework to provide modern,
OL,16,Fconsistent regulation for burial and
OL,17,Fcremation," she said.
OL,19,FPublic consultation on the proposed
OL,20,Fchanges is open until January 2025.
